---
title: Black Bean & Charred Bell Pepper Quesadillas with Caramelized Onion and Crisp Romaine Salad
description: Crisp flour tortillas are stuffed with refried beans, sautéed onion, fresh garlic and bell peppers. Gooey, melted mozzarella ties everything together, and a crisp side salad cools it all down.
